SWORD SLINGING
Type: Combat Action
See also: <help combat actions>

You are a vicious master of the sword, cutting down enemies before 
they have a chance to react. Experienced sword slingers strike with 
greater force and accuracy with each foe they fell, turning themselves
into a whirlwind of deadly steel.

The fighting style of sword slinging is rumored to be taught by a 
certain wandering ronin of Tai Ri.

Sword Slinging allows the following verbs:
1   : run (target) through
50  : intercept (target)
100 : cut (target) down
150 : reap (target)
300 : whirlwind
